=== 编剧 ===
《X档案》主创克里斯·卡特为本集编剧，称“这就是结局，不会再有转机，所以必须竭尽全力做好。有不少内容令人分心，忽视实际情况，一切都在瓦解。”<ref name="Hurwitz-Knowles">{{Cite book | title = The Complete X-Files | first1 = Matt | last1 = Hurwitz | first2 = Chris | last2 = Knowles | publisher = Insight Editions | year = 2008 | isbn = 978-1933784809 | pages = }}</ref>{{rp|209–216}}他还称“该是时候了，知道这是最后一次看到斯嘉丽和穆德时再来编剧感觉很奇怪”<ref name="truthtruth" />。执行制作人[[弗兰克·斯伯特尼|弗兰克·斯伯特尼]]（{{lang|en|Frank Spotnitz}}）表示，卡特已在2002年初公布电视剧收尾的消息，给予大家充分时间思考和计划大结局，给予所有角色应得的待遇<ref name="truthtruth" />。安娜贝丝·吉什（{{lang|en|Annabeth Gish}}）事后对节目体面收尾表示满意<ref name="reflect" />。本集出演约翰·菲茨杰拉德·拜尔斯（{{lang|en|John Fitzgerald Byers}}）的布鲁斯·哈伍德（{{lang|en|Bruce Harwood}}）称大结局堪称“一代人的过去”<ref name="reflect">{{cite AV media | people = Rabwin, Paul | year = 2002 | title = Reflections on the Truth | location = The X-Files: The Complete Ninth Season | medium = DVD | publisher = 20th Century Fox Home Entertainment}}</ref>。

《真相》有许多过往分集的元素，结尾穆德和斯嘉丽在旅馆房间交谈与[[试播集_(X档案)|全剧开局]]很相似<ref name="Kessenich-2002">{{cite book | last = Kessenich | first = Tom | title = Examination: An Unauthorized Look at Seasons 6–9 of the X-Files | publisher = Trafford Publishing | year = 2002 | isbn = 978-1553698128 | access-date = 2021-03-31 | url = https://archive.org/details/examinationsunau0000kess}}</ref>{{rp|211}}<ref>{{cite news | last = Rahman | first = Ray | title = Chris Carter Looks Back at 'The X-Files' Series Finale: 'We Really Came of Age with the Internet' | url = https://ew.com/article/2014/04/16/x-files-finale-chris-carter/ | date = 2014-04-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210120013841/https://ew.com/article/2014/04/16/x-files-finale-chris-carter/ | access-date = 2021-03-31 | work = [[娱乐周刊|Entertainment Weekly]] | publisher = [[華納媒體|Time Warner]] | dead-url = no | archive-date = 2021-01-20 }}</ref>。癌人向穆德揭示的“真相”是外星人计划在2012年12月22日殖民地球，剧中还称这是[[玛雅人|玛雅人]]的预测<ref name="Bush-2008" />{{rp|58}}<ref name="truthepisode">{{cite episode | title = The Truth | credits = Kim Manners (director); Chris Carter (writer) | series = The X-Files | series-link = X档案 | network = Fox | season = 9 | number = 19 & 20}}</ref><ref name="shear">{{cite book | year = 2009 | first1 = Robert | last1 = Shearman | first2 = Lars | last2 = Pearson | title = Wanting to Believe: A Critical Guide to The X-Files, Millennium & The Lone Gunmen | publisher = Mad Norwegian Press | isbn = 978-0975944691 | pages = 278–280}}</ref>，这又与[[X档案_(第二季)|第二季]]第十集《[[红色博物馆|红色博物馆]]》（{{lang|en|''Red Museum''}}）联系起来，该集的[[新興宗教|新興宗教]]成员深信2012年将拉开新时代<ref name="Bush-2008">{{cite book | title = Myth-X | last = Bush | first = Michelle | isbn = 978-1435746886 | year = 2008 | publisher = Lulu}}</ref>{{rp|58}}<ref>{{Cite episode | title = Red Museum |credits = Win Phelps (director); Chris Carter (writer) | series = The X-Files | network = Fox | season =3 | number = 10}}</ref>。

卡特在2008年电影《[[X檔案：我要相信|X檔案：我要相信]]》上映前表示，如果票房理想，可能会取材《真相》揭示的外星人入侵拍摄第三部《X档案》系列电影<ref>{{cite news | url = https://ew.com/comic-con/2008/04/18/chris-carter-wa/ | title = 'X-Files' Creator Chris Carter Wants to Believe in a Third Movie featuring Mulder and Scully | last = Collis | first = Clark | publisher = [[时代公司|Time Inc]] | work = [[娱乐周刊|Entertainment Weekly]] | date = 2008-03-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190514191018/https://ew.com/comic-con/2008/04/18/chris-carter-wa/ | access-date = 2021-03-31 | archive-date = 2019-05-14 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。电影上映后，卡特、斯伯特尼、杜考夫尼和安德森都表示有兴趣参与下一部电影<ref>{{cite web | last = Gallman | first = Brett | title = Frank Spotnitz Still Wants to Do a Third 'X-Files' Film | url = https://movies.yahoo.com/news/frank-spotnitz-still-wants-third-x-files-film-194700012.html | website = Yahoo! Movies | publisher = [[雅虎|Yahoo!]] | access-date = 2013-12-14 | date = 2012-08-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131214190840/https://movies.yahoo.com/news/frank-spotnitz-still-wants-third-x-files-film-194700012.html | archive-date = 2013-12-14 | dead-url = yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = 'X-Files' Movie: David Duchovny Is In | url = https://www.huffpost.com/entry/x-files-movie-david-duchovny_n_1770682 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210308132855/https://www.huffpost.com/entry/x-files-movie-david-duchovny_n_1770682 | access-date = 2021-03-31 | newspaper = [[赫芬顿邮报|The Huffington Post]] | publisher = [[美国在线|AOL]] | date = 2012-08-12 | archive-date = 2021-03-08 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | last = Marcus | first = Stephanie | title = Gillian Anderson: 'X-Files 3' Movie Is 'Looking Pretty Good' | newspaper = The Huffington Post | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210309064220/https://www.huffpost.com/entry/gillian-anderson-x-files-3-movie_n_1833518 | url = https://www.huffpost.com/entry/gillian-anderson-x-files-3-movie_n_1833518 | access-date = 2021-03-31 | publisher = AOL | date = 2012-